<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Quiz — Manajemen Proyek Perangkat Lunak</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Outfit:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&family=Manrope:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --bg: #0a0a0a;
    --surface: #141414;
    --surface-light: #1a1a1a;
    --border: #2a2a2a;
    --border-light: #333333;
    --text: #f5f5f5;
    --text-muted: #888888;
    --accent: #FF3D00; /* Vibrant orange-red */
    --accent-hover: #FF5722;
    --success: #00C853;
    --error: #FF1744;
    --warning: #FFD600;
  }

  * {
    box-sizing: border-box;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
  }

  body {
    font-family: 'Manrope', -apple-system, sans-serif;
    background: var(--bg);
    color: var(--text);
    min-height: 100vh;
    padding: clamp(16px, 4vw, 40px) clamp(12px, 3vw, 20px);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .app {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    width: 100%;
  }

  /* Header */
  .header {
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding-bottom: clamp(20px, 5vw, 32px);
    margin-bottom: clamp(24px, 6vw, 40px);
  }

  .header-brand {
    font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(10px, 2.5vw, 12px);
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: clamp(2px, 0.5vw, 3px);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: clamp(6px, 2vw, 8px);
  }

  .header h1 {
    font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(28px, 6vw, 56px);
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1.1;
    margin-bottom: clamp(12px, 3vw, 16px);
    letter-spacing: clamp(-1.5px, -0.3vw, -2px);
  }

  .header h1 span {
    color: var(--accent);
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .header-topics {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 8px;
  }

  .topic {
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 500;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    padding: 6px 12px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 100px;
  }

  /* Stats Bar */
  .stats-bar {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 1px;
    background: var(--border);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }

  .stat {
    background: var(--surface);
    padding: 20px 24px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .stat-label {
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .stat-value {
    font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
    font-size: 28px;
    font-weight: 300;
    letter-spacing: -1px;
  }

  .stat-value.accent {
    color: var(--accent);
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  /* Progress Bar */
  .progress-section {
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }

  .progress-info {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .progress-label {
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  .progress-track {
    height: 2px;
    background: var(--border);
    position: relative;
  }

  .progress-bar {
    height: 100%;
    background: var(--accent);
    transition: width 0.5s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
  }

  /* Question Navigation */
  .question-nav {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(36px, 1fr));
    gap: 2px;
    background: var(--border);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    margin-bottom: clamp(24px, 5vw, 40px);
  }

  .nav-dot {
    aspect-ratio: 1;
    min-height: 36px;
    background: var(--surface);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: clamp(10px, 2.5vw, 11px);
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
    user-select: none;
    -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;
  }

  .nav-dot:hover {
    background: var(--surface-light);
  }

  .nav-dot.current {
    background: var(--accent);
    color: var(--bg);
  }

  .nav-dot.answered {
    background: var(--surface-light);
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .nav-dot.answered.current {
    background: var(--accent);
  }

  .nav-dot.wrong {
    background: var(--error);
    color: var(--bg);
  }

  /* Question Card */
  .card {
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 40px;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .card-header {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
    padding-bottom: 24px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .question-number {
    font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  .question-number span {
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  .question-text {
    font-size: clamp(16px, 4vw, 18px);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: clamp(20px, 5vw, 32px);
    color: var(--text);
  }

  /* Options */
  .options {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2px;
  }

  .option {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 48px 1fr;
    gap: 20px;
    padding: 20px 24px;
    background: var(--surface-light);
    border: 1px solid transparent;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
  }

  .option:hover:not(.disabled) {
    background: var(--border-light);
  }

  .option.selected {
    background: var(--border-light);
    border-color: var(--border);
  }

  .option.correct {
    background: rgba(0, 200, 83, 0.1);
    border-color: var(--success);
  }

  .option.correct .option-letter {
    background: var(--success);
    color: var(--bg);
  }

  .option.wrong {
    background: rgba(255, 23, 68, 0.1);
    border-color: var(--error);
  }

  .option.wrong .option-letter {
    background: var(--error);
    color: var(--bg);
  }

  .option.disabled {
    cursor: default;
  }

  .option-letter {
    font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    background: var(--border);
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 600;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .option-text {
    font-size: clamp(14px, 2.5vw, 15px);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.5;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    word-wrap: break-word;
    overflow-wrap: break-word;
  }

  /* Explanation */
  .explain {
    margin-top: 32px;
    padding: 24px;
    border-left: 2px solid var(--border);
    background: var(--surface-light);
    display: none;
  }

  .explain.show {
    display: block;
    animation: fadeIn 0.3s ease;
  }

  @keyframes fadeIn {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(-8px); }
    to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }

  .explain.correct {
    border-color: var(--success);
  }

  .explain.wrong {
    border-color: var(--error);
  }

  .explain-label {
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .explain-text {
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  /* Navigation */
  .nav {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 16px;
  }

  button {
    font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(11px, 2.5vw, 12px);
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: clamp(14px, 3vw, 16px) clamp(24px, 5vw, 32px);
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    color: var(--text);
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
    min-height: 48px;
    min-width: 120px;
    -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;
  }

  button:hover:not(:disabled) {
    background: var(--border-light);
    border-color: var(--border-light);
  }

  button:disabled {
    opacity: 0.3;
    cursor: not-allowed;
  }

  button.primary {
    background: var(--accent);
    border-color: var(--accent);
    color: var(--bg);
  }

  button.primary:hover:not(:disabled) {
    background: var(--accent-hover);
    border-color: var(--accent-hover);
  }

  /* Result Screen */
  .result {
    text-align: center;
    padding: clamp(32px, 8vw, 60px) clamp(20px, 5vw, 40px);
  }

  .result-brand {
    font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: clamp(16px, 4vw, 24px);
  }

  .result h2 {
    font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(32px, 7vw, 72px);
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1.1;
    margin-bottom: clamp(12px, 3vw, 16px);
    letter-spacing: -1.5px;
  }

  .result .score {
    font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(48px, 12vw, 120px);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--accent);
    line-height: 1;
    margin: clamp(24px, 6vw, 32px) 0;
  }

  .score-label {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  .result-stats {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 2px;
    background: var(--border);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    margin: 40px 0;
  }

  .result-stat {
    background: var(--surface);
    padding: 24px;
  }

  .result-stat-value {
    font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
    font-size: 32px;
    font-weight: 300;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }

  .result-stat.correct .result-stat-value {
    color: var(--success);
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .result-stat.wrong .result-stat-value {
    color: var(--error);
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .result-stat-label {
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  .result-message {
    font-size: 16px;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.7;
    max-width: 480px;
    margin: 0 auto 40px;
  }

  /* Utility */
  .hidden {
    display: none !important;
  }

  /* Keyboard hints */
  .keyboard-hint {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 24px;
    margin-top: 32px;
    padding: 16px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .keyboard-hint span {
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  .key {
    font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 600;
    min-width: 28px;
    height: 28px;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    background: var(--border);
    color: var(--text);
  }

  /* Responsive */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .header {
      padding-bottom: 24px;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }

    .header-brand {
      font-size: 10px;
      letter-spacing: 2px;
    }

    .stats-bar {
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }

    .stat {
      padding: 16px 20px;
    }

    .stat-value {
      font-size: clamp(24px, 5vw, 28px);
    }

    .progress-section {
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }

    .question-nav {
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }

    .card {
      padding: 24px;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    .card-header {
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      padding-bottom: 16px;
    }

    .question-text {
      font-size: 16px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .option {
      gap: 16px;
      padding: 16px 20px;
    }

    .option-letter {
      width: 44px;
      height: 44px;
      font-size: 15px;
    }

    .explain {
      margin-top: 20px;
      padding: 20px;
    }

    .keyboard-hint {
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 12px;
      padding: 12px;
    }

    .keyboard-hint span:first-child {
      width: 100%;
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .result {
      padding: 40px 24px;
    }

    .result h2 {
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }

    .result-stats {
      margin: 24px 0;
      gap: 1px;
    }

    .result-stat {
      padding: 20px 16px;
    }

    .result-message {
      font-size: 15px;
      margin-bottom: 32px;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .stats-bar {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2px;
    }

    .stat {
      padding: 14px 16px;
    }

    .nav {
      flex-direction: column-reverse;
      gap: 12px;
    }

    .nav button {
      width: 100%;
    }

    .result-stats {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .option {
      grid-template-columns: 40px 1fr;
      gap: 12px;
      padding: 14px 16px;
    }

    .option-letter {
      width: 40px;
      height: 40px;
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .header-topics {
      gap: 6px;
    }

    .topic {
      font-size: 9px;
      padding: 4px 10px;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .card {
      padding: 20px 16px;
    }

    .card-header {
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      padding-bottom: 12px;
    }

    .question-text {
      font-size: 15px;
    }

    .option {
      padding: 12px 14px;
    }

    .option-letter {
      width: 36px;
      height: 36px;
      font-size: 13px;
    }

    .option-text {
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .explain {
      padding: 16px;
      margin-top: 16px;
    }

    .explain-text {
      font-size: 13px;
    }

    .result {
      padding: 32px 20px;
    }

    .result-stat-value {
      font-size: 28px;
    }

    .key {
      min-width: 24px;
      height: 24px;
      font-size: 11px;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 360px) {
    body {
      padding: 12px;
    }

    .card {
      padding: 16px 12px;
    }

    .option {
      grid-template-columns: 32px 1fr;
      padding: 10px 12px;
    }

    .option-letter {
      width: 32px;
      height: 32px;
      font-size: 12px;
    }

    .question-nav {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(32px, 1fr));
    }

    .nav-dot {
      min-height: 32px;
      font-size: 9px;
    }
  }

  /* Focus styles */
  button:focus-visible,
  .option:focus-visible,
  .nav-dot:focus-visible {
    outline: 2px solid var(--accent);
    outline-offset: 2px;
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="app">

  <header class="header">
    <div class="header-brand">SIR207 — Kuis 2</div>
    <h1>Manajemen <span>Proyek</span></h1>
    <div class="header-topics">
      <span class="topic">Risk Management</span>
      <span class="topic">Quality Management</span>
      <span class="topic">Schedule</span>
      <span class="topic">Project Closure</span>
      <span class="topic">Change Control</span>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="stats-bar">
    <div class="stat">
      <div class="stat-label">Soal</div>
      <div class="stat-value" id="currentStat">1<span style="font-size: 16px; color: var(--text-muted);">/37</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="stat">
      <div class="stat-label">Skor</div>
      <div class="stat-value accent" id="scoreStat">0</div>
    </div>
    <div class="stat">
      <div class="stat-label">Dijawab</div>
      <div class="stat-value" id="answeredStat">0</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="progress-section">
    <div class="progress-info">
      <span class="progress-label" id="progressLabel">Kemajuan</span>
      <span class="progress-label" id="progressPercent">0%</span>
    </div>
    <div class="progress-track">
      <div class="progress-bar" id="progressFill"></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="question-nav" id="questionNav"></div>

  <div id="quizArea"></div>

  <div id="resultArea" class="card result hidden">
    <div class="result-brand">Hasil Kuis 2</div>
    <h2 id="resultTitle">Selesai</h2>
    <div class="score">
      <span id="scoreText">0</span>
      <span class="score-label">/ 37</span>
    </div>
    <p class="result-message" id="resultDesc"></p>

    <div class="result-stats">
      <div class="result-stat correct">
        <div class="result-stat-value" id="correctCount">0</div>
        <div class="result-stat-label">Benar</div>
      </div>
      <div class="result-stat wrong">
        <div class="result-stat-value" id="wrongCount">0</div>
        <div class="result-stat-label">Salah</div>
      </div>
      <div class="result-stat">
        <div class="result-stat-value" id="accuracy">0%</div>
        <div class="result-stat-label">Akurasi</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="nav" style="justify-content: center;">
      <button class="primary" onclick="restartQuiz()">Ulangi Kuis</button>
    </div>
  </div>

</div>

<script>
const questions = [
  {
    q: "Lag time adalah:",
    opts: [
      "Total waktu proyek",
      "Waktu ekstra untuk menyelesaikan aktivitas",
      "Slack total proyek",
      "Durasi kegiatan",
      "Waktu minimum antar dua aktivitas"
    ],
    correct: 1,
    explain: "Lag time adalah penundaan yang disengaja antara dua aktivitas yang saling bergantung — waktu ekstra sebelum aktivitas berikutnya bisa dimulai."
  },
  {
    q: "Plan-Do-Check-Act (PDCA) adalah pendekatan dalam:",
    opts: [
      "Quality management",
      "Risk management",
      "Time management",
      "Communication management",
      "Cost control"
    ],
    correct: 0,
    explain: "PDCA (siklus Deming) adalah inti dari quality management / manajemen kualitas untuk perbaikan berkelanjutan."
  },
  {
    q: "Teknik apa yang digunakan untuk menghitung dampak risiko secara numerik terhadap tujuan proyek?",
    opts: [
      "Risk Treatment (Menangani Risiko)",
      "Perform Quantitative Risk Analysis (Melakukan Analisis Risiko Kuantitatif)",
      "Brainstorming (Curah Pendapat)",
      "Expert Judgment (Pertimbangan Ahli)",
      "SWOT Analysis (Analisis SWOT)"
    ],
    correct: 1,
    explain: "Perform Quantitative Risk Analysis menggunakan angka/probabilitas untuk menghitung dampak risiko terhadap tujuan proyek (contoh: Monte Carlo, EMV)."
  },
  {
    q: "Selama penutupan proyek, sponsor meminta laporan akhir yang membandingkan hasil aktual dengan target biaya, jadwal, dan ruang lingkup. Tujuan utama laporan tersebut adalah:",
    opts: [
      "Mengevaluasi kinerja proyek secara keseluruhan",
      "Menentukan anggaran proyek berikutnya",
      "Mengembangkan WBS baru",
      "Mengidentifikasi stakeholder baru",
      "Menentukan reward dan punishment"
    ],
    correct: 0,
    explain: "Laporan akhir yang membandingkan aktual vs target bertujuan untuk mengevaluasi performa/kinerja proyek secara keseluruhan."
  },
  {
    q: "Seorang manajer proyek menemukan bahwa seluruh deliverable telah selesai, tetapi pelanggan belum memberikan persetujuan akhir. Apa yang sebaiknya dilakukan?",
    opts: [
      "Membubarkan tim proyek segera",
      "Menunggu dan memperoleh penerimaan formal dari pelanggan",
      "Melakukan pengujian tambahan",
      "Menutup proyek karena pekerjaan telah selesai",
      "Menghapus dokumentasi proyek"
    ],
    correct: 1,
    explain: "Proyek belum bisa ditutup tanpa formal acceptance dari pelanggan. Persetujuan formal adalah syarat wajib sebelum project closure."
  },
  {
    q: "Dokumen pelajaran yang dipetik dalam proyek disebut:",
    opts: [
      "Issue log",
      "Lessons learned",
      "Project notebook",
      "Control sheet",
      "Risk register"
    ],
    correct: 1,
    explain: "Lessons learned adalah dokumen yang mencatat pelajaran/pengalaman yang dipetik selama proyek untuk referensi proyek mendatang."
  },
  {
    q: "Seorang pelanggan menerima sistem yang telah memenuhi seluruh spesifikasi teknis, tetapi antarmukanya sulit digunakan sehingga tidak memenuhi harapan pengguna. Pelajaran utama dari kasus ini adalah:",
    opts: [
      "Memenuhi persyaratan teknis belum tentu memenuhi kebutuhan pelanggan",
      "Kualitas hanya ditentukan oleh spesifikasi teknis",
      "Jadwal proyek lebih penting daripada kualitas",
      "Pengujian harus dilakukan untuk semua kriteria kualitas",
      "Pengujian tidak diperlukan"
    ],
